    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove all tax reliefs granted to all religious groups",
        "additional_details": "Religious groups control significant wealth and in a secular modern society serve a declining group of people in relative terms. Property taxes such as council tax should be levied to provide much needed local tax incomes for councils. ",
        "background": "Remove tax reliefs afforded to religious groups such that they pay business rates on commercial activity and all normal property taxes and council taxes on properties occupied for religious purposes.",
